---
import Header from "@/components/Header.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "@/styles/globals.css";
---

<Layout title="Frontend Mentor | News homepage">
  <Header />
  <main class="mx-4 mb-[4.69rem] xl:mb-[7.75rem] xl:mx-[10.31rem]">
    <section class="flex flex-col gap-16 xl:flex-row xl:gap-[1.87rem]">
      <div class="xl:w-[45.625rem]">
        <picture>
          <source
            media="(min-width:768px )"
            srcset="/images/image-web-3-desktop.jpg"
          />
          <img
            src="/images/image-web-3-mobile.jpg"
            alt="image-web-3"
            class=""
          />
        </picture>
        <div
          class="flex flex-col gap-4 xl:flex-row xl:gap-[1.87rem] mt-6 xl:mt-8"
        >
          <h1
            class="xl:w-[21.875rem] w-[21.4375rem] text-[2.5rem] font-extrabold leading-10 xl:text-[3.5rem] xl:leading-[3.5rem] text-[#00001A]"
          >
            The Bright Future of Web 3.0?
          </h1>
          <div
            class="flex flex-col gap-6 xl:w-[21.875rem] xl:gap-[1.81rem] w-[21.4375rem]"
          >
            <p
              class="text-[#5E607A] text-[0.9375rem] font-normal leading-relaxed"
            >
              We dive into the next evolution of the web that claims to put the
              power of the platforms back into the hands of the people. But is
              it really fulfilling its promise?
            </p>
            <button
              type="button"
              class="w-[11.5625rem] outline-none h-12 bg-[#F15D51] uppercase text-sm leading-6 font-bold tracking-[0.27344rem] text-[#FFFDFA] hover:bg-[#00001A] transition-colors ease-linear duration-500"
              >READ MORE</button
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="xl:w-[21.875rem] bg-[#00001A] py-6 pl-[1.31rem] pr-7 xl:px-6 xl:py-8 flex flex-col gap-[2.19rem] xl:gap-[2.12rem]"
      >
        <h2
          class="text-[#E9AA52] text-[2rem] font-bold leading-8 xl:text-[2.5rem] xl:leading-10"
        >
          New
        </h2>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-[3.81rem]">
          <div
            class="flex flex-col gap-2 relative after:absolute after:w-[18.875rem] after:h-[0.0625rem] after:bg-[#5E607A] after:left-0 after:right-0 after:-bottom-[1.81rem]"
          >
            <h3
              class="text-xl leading-6 font-extrabold text-[#FFFDFA] hover:text-[#E9AA52] transition-colors duration-500 ease-linear"
            >
              Hydrogen VS Electric Cars
            </h3>
            <p
              class="text-[#C5C6CE] text-[0.9375rem] font-normal leading-relaxed"
            >
              Will hydrogen-fueled cars ever catch up to EVs?
            </p>
          </div>
          <div
            class="flex flex-col gap-2 relative after:absolute after:w-[18.875rem] after:h-[0.0625rem] after:bg-[#5E607A] after:left-0 after:right-0 after:-bottom-[1.81rem]"
          >
            <h3
              class="text-xl leading-6 font-extrabold text-[#FFFDFA] hover:text-[#E9AA52] transition-colors duration-500 ease-linear"
            >
              The Downsides of AI Artistry
            </h3>
            <p
              class="text-[#C5C6CE] text-[0.9375rem] font-normal leading-relaxed"
            >
              What are the possible adverse effects of on-demand AI image
              generation?
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
            <h3
              class="text-xl leading-6 font-extrabold text-[#FFFDFA] hover:text-[#E9AA52] transition-colors duration-500 ease-linear"
            >
              Is VC Funding Drying Up?
            </h3>
            <p
              class="text-[#C5C6CE] text-[0.9375rem] font-normal leading-relaxed"
            >
              Private funding by VC firms is down 50% YOY. We take a look at
              what that means.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section
      class="mt-20 mb-[4.69rem] xl:mt-[4.5rem] xl:mb-[7.75rem] flex flex-col gap-8 xl:flex-row xl:justify-center xl:items-center"
    >
      <!-- Retro PCs -->
      <div class="flex gap-8">
        <div class="">
          <img
            src="/images/image-retro-pcs.jpg"
            alt=""
            class="w-[11.90625rem] h-[7.9375rem]"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col">
          <h3 class="text-[#C5C6CE] text-[2rem] font-bold leading-8 mb-3">
            01
          </h3>
          <h4
            class="text-[#00001A] text-lg leading-6 font-extrabold mb-[0.56rem] hover:text-[#F15D51] transition-colors ease-linear duration-500"
          >
            Reviving Retro PCs
          </h4>
          <p
            class="text-[0.9375rem] text-[#5E607A] font-normal leading-relaxed"
          >
            What happens when old PCs are given modern upgrades?
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Top 10 Laptops  -->
      <div class="flex gap-8">
        <div class="">
          <img
            src="/images/image-top-laptops.jpg"
            alt=""
            class="xl:w-[11.90625rem] h-[7.9375rem] w-[10rem]"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col">
          <h3 class="text-[#C5C6CE] text-[2rem] font-bold leading-8 mb-3">
            02
          </h3>
          <h4
            class="text-[#00001A] text-lg leading-6 font-extrabold mb-[0.56rem] hover:text-[#F15D51] transition-colors ease-linear duration-500"
          >
            Top 10 Laptops
          </h4>
          <p
            class="text-[0.9375rem] text-[#5E607A] font-normal leading-relaxed"
          >
            Our best picks for various needs and budgets.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Growth of Gaming -->
      <div class="flex gap-8">
        <div class="">
          <img
            src="/images/image-gaming-growth.jpg"
            alt=""
            class="w-[11.90625rem] h-[7.9375rem]"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col">
          <h3 class="text-[#C5C6CE] text-[2rem] font-bold leading-8 mb-3">
            03
          </h3>
          <h4
            class="text-[#00001A] text-lg leading-6 font-extrabold mb-[0.56rem] hover:text-[#F15D51] transition-colors ease-linear duration-500"
          >
            The Growth of Gaming
          </h4>
          <p
            class="text-[0.9375rem] text-[#5E607A] font-normal leading-relaxed"
          >
            How the pandemic has sparked fresh opportunities.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

